  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "MinCutPool (Bianchi et al. 2020) implements the learning of node soft assignment matrix using a multilayer perceptron.",
    "Deep Modularity Network (DMoN) (Tsitsulin et al. 2023) uses the null model to optimize the node soft assignment matrix and thus control the inhomogeneity in the graph.",
    "HAP (Liu et al. 2021a) proposes a novel graph schema attribute extraction technique a cross-level attention mechanism to achieve the learning of soft assignment matrix.",
    "SEP (Wu et al. 2022a) achieves the learning of node soft assignment matrix through structural entropy minimization.",
    "In general, although graph pooling strategies based on node clustering have shown certain effects in graph-level tasks, such methods usually rely on soft assignment matrix for node classification, which is difficult to deal with large-scale graph data in the real world."
